<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="description" content="Ferramenta de investigação OSINT e hacking ético.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="OSINT, hacking ético, investigação, cibersegurança">
    <meta name="author" content="Seu Nome">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OSINT_Hub</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: background-image: url('/static/dragao_kali.jpg'); /* Ajustado para voltar ao diretório pai */
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .header-line {
            background-color: #ff0000;
            height: 5px;
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .header-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #ff0000;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }
        .detective-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #ff0000;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        .main-container {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-top: 120px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #d3d3d3;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .tool-btn {
            background-color: #000000;
            border: 2px solid #ff0000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 250px;
            display: block;
            text-align: left;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .tool-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }
        .tool-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff0000;
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }
        .tool-btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }
        .right-panel {
            position: fixed;
            top: 120px;
            right: 20px;
            width: 300px;
        }
        .status-panel, .terminal {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .status-panel h3, .terminal h3 {
            color: #ff0000;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .terminal pre {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #00ff00;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .right-panel {
                position: static;
                width: 100%;
                margin-top: 40px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-line"></div>
        <div class="header-container">
            <i class="fas fa-user-secret detective-icon"></i>
            <a href="/" class="logo">OSINT_Hub</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="main-container">
            <h1 class="title">OSINT Investigator</h1>
            <p class="description">Ferramentas de Investigação e Hacking Ético</p>
            <div>
                <a href="/theharvester" class="btn tool-btn">Iniciar Investigação</a>
                <a href="/sherlock" class="btn tool-btn">Busca de Perfis</a>
                <a href="/phoneinfoga" class="btn tool-btn">Info de Telefone</a>
                <a href="/whois" class="btn tool-btn">Consulta Whois</a>
                <a href="/exiftool" class="btn tool-btn">Extrair Metadados</a>
                <a href="/nmap" class="btn tool-btn">Escanear Rede</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-panel">
            <div class="status-panel">
                <h3>Status do Sistema</h3>
                <p><strong>Conexão:</strong> Ativa</p>
                <p><strong>Última Verificação:</strong> 5 minutos atrás</p>
                <p><strong>Notícias:</strong> <a href="#">Novo ataque cibernético detectado</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal">
                <h3>Logs do Sistema</h3>
                <pre>
                    <code>
[INFO] Iniciando escaneamento de rede...
[SUCCESS] 5 dispositivos encontrados.
[WARNING] 1 dispositivo com vulnerabilidades.
                    </code>
                </pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.tool-btn').forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', () => {
                alert(`Você clicou em: ${button.textContent}`);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
